{
  "stem": "888.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, and once I got married, and had a family, I mean, things came a little easier.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, it came easier.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But also, you know, there was many, many days I was just not feeling well, not knowing-- you know, being depressed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And you know, that's, that's mainly-- and of course, you know, from time to time, you know, you watched certain things which remind you.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you kind of carry it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, also I think we have a lot of anger also.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, well, you know, you're angry at the Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you don't necessarily pick one person out and say, I'm angry at him because he's Hungarian, or I'm angry at him because he's German.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But in general, you understand, I am.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I feel a lot of anger towards them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, you know, like for instance these particular camps, you know, like Auschwitz, we didn't-- we weren't sort of forced into, into labor.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You understand?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it was in the summertime.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the hunger started just, just before.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they took us to Gross-Rosen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they started giving you a portion of this, and a portion of that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you realized, you know, as soon as you ate, you were hungry before and you were hungry-- you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean-- and then later on, of course, they didn't give you any, any substantial food at all.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So there you were constantly just starving.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, they took us to Gross-Rosen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, they made a-- they, they re-- you know, they take you--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, first you come over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
